quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  92,19,"Isagoo uusan jirin cid ku leh abaal uu u gudayo."
  92,20,"Waxse u bixiya doonista Wejiga Rabbigi, ee Sarreeya."
  92,21,"Wuu raalli noqon doonaa qofkaasi."
  96,7,"Markuu isku ogaado Hodantinnimo iyo deeqtoonaan."
  96,8,"Hubaal! Waa xagga (Alle) Rabbigaa noqodku."
  96,9,"Ka warran midka ka reeba."
  97,4,"Malaa’igta iyo Jabriil baa la soo dega (habeenkaa) Idanka Rabbigood arrin walba oo xukun ah,"
  97,5,"Nabad weeye (habeenkaa) ilaa waagu ka baryo{2}.",footnotes:1:. Rasuulkii Alle s.c.w. wuxuu yidhi: Ka doondoona layaltul Qadarka tirooyinka is dheer ee tobanka habeenood ee u dambeeya Ramadaanka.,footnotes:2:
  98,1,"Kuwa gaaloobay oo ka mid ah ehlu Kitaabka (Yuhuudda iyo Nasaarada) iyo mushrikiinta ma ahayn kuwa ka tagaya (gaalnimadooda) intay uga timaado xujada cad."
  98,2,"Rasuul (Muxammad) ka socda xagga Alle oo akhriyaya waraaqo daahir ah."
  98,3,"Ay ku yaallaan xukunno wanaagsan."